## Third-Party Tools

This software automatically downloads and uses the following third-party tools
at runtime. These tools are not bundled with this application and are subject
to their own licenses:

- **yt-dlp** (https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp) — The Unlicense
  Downloaded from: https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp/releases/latest

- **FFmpeg** (https://ffmpeg.org) — GNU Lesser General Public License v2.1+
  Downloaded from: https://www.gyan.dev/ffmpeg/builds/

The authors of this software claim no ownership over yt-dlp or FFmpeg.
All rights to these tools remain with their respective authors.
